# 09-eval-run.gif — the eval campaign as it actually ran (S7 Task 8).
# Replays the REAL grounded-arm log from the 2026-07-10 live campaign
# (eval/out/live-backup-2026-07-09/run_grounded_live.log) with real
# commands over the real file — never a fabricated transcript.
#
# Render from the repo root:  vhs web/tools/eval-run.tape
Output docs/media/09-eval-run.gif
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 800
Set Height 500
Set Padding 14
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Type "# the grounded arm of the live eval campaign, as logged (2026-07-09):"
Enter
Type "head -5 eval/out/live-backup-2026-07-09/run_grounded_live.log"
Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "tail -5 eval/out/live-backup-2026-07-09/run_grounded_live.log"
Enter
Sleep 7s
